						   <tr><td valign=top><img src='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/monsterpics/A_Crag_Spider.JPG' alt="Picture of A Crag Spider" align=RIGHT>
Loot:  Spider Legs (drops about 1/3 of the time)<br><br>Loot:  Venom sack (drops about 1/3 of the time, when dropped, usually one but have seen two)<br><br>Loot:  Spider silk (drops about 80% of the of time, ranges from 2-8 silk )<br><br>Loot:  Research items (drops about 1/5 of the time, so far have seen runes, pages of Tsarin (sp?), and words.  Also have twice received Ice of Velious (mage research item).<br><br>Loot info from Salenie Silkweaver </td></tr><tr><td valign=top><b>Minimum Level</b>: 18 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Maximum Level</b>:20 </td></tr><tr><td><b>Known Habitats</b>:</td></tr><tr><td><li><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/EKarana.htm'>Eastern Karana</a></li></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 align=right style='font-size:9px;'><a href="mailto:illia@allakhazam.com?Subject=Correction for A Crag Spider&Body=On the page: http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=385

