	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>You will have difficulty with the Crags as a Wiz at 18.  Go back to N. Karana and fatten up on Borer's and Griffawns.  At 19, Borers and Griffs still give good ep.  But nothing compared to Crags.  Almost a full blue bar per kill.<br><br>Same old trick of root and nuke but as for your mathematical manna bubble.  Make sure you have Resistant skin on which increases poison resistance in case the crag gets close enough. Against a single crag, you have enough manna to cast root on it 4 times and 1 partial or complete resist on your lightning bolt with 142 INT before you go oom. Please adjust if you have lesser INT. Laugh if you have more. since Crags for some reason, even though they don't resist root, they break of off it faster than any mobs at this level.<br><br>At 19, I am able to blast away for the full damage of the Lightning bolt at 123 dmg.  So 3 bolts and a Lightning shock takes care of it.  Fight shouldn't last for more than 15 seconds.<br><br>Once you make 20, go back and get your new spells... Now you can Teleport... Weeee.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
